mars in virgo for this august reminds us how the smallest decisions, built up over and over, can lead to large impact

and that an intentionally sharp moment can be more effective than a disorganized energetic frenzy 

the precision of virgo turns the martian weapon into more of a scalpel and less of a machete in this sign

so, little by little, with mindfulness, we can build up momentum that amounts to a large-scale change in the world around us. 

x

soon
